Guitar Gift-Giving Guide
: Headstock Smartphone Holder Among the more practical gifts for guitarists (or yourself) this holiday season are smartphone holders that attach to the headstock. Excellent for keeping chord changes, words, charts, or your email handy. There are a number of different models available, most of which clip on, including the Griffin Sidekick and the Castiv. They run from about $20 to $35.
All those things you want for yourself (or for every other guitarist).

Folkies
Folkie Quiz of the Day: This influential political folk group was together only 1941-1942. During that short time it had as many as 15 members, but only 5 or 6 usually performed at any time. Among its core members were Woody Guthrie (back row center) and Pete Seeger (front row right). Who will be the first person to correctly identify this group? Extra credit: Who can name the other three people shown in this photo?
Photos from my Folkie Quiz of the Day series.
